text: Roaches may refer to: * Carl Roaches (born 1953), a former American football player * The Roaches, a gritstone escarpment in Staffordshire, England * Rutilus or roaches, a genus of fishes * Plural of "roach", another name for cockroach ==See also== * Roach (disambiguation) * The Roches, a female vocal group
title: Roaches
